    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Correct. The mission is officially being concluded due to power constraints. Before we finalize the shutdown sequence, please generate a high-level summary of the scientific value lost by this early termination versus the intended mission duration. We need to document the reason for the cessation of data collection.",
